replies.body:
Crashes in champion select are often caused by an unstable connection to the server. Due to the other *lag* spikes you've been getting as well, I think this is very likely to be caused by a local network connection issue. To confirm your local settings are good, I recommend working through the steps in our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps caused any change.
